{"tid":518569,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[intel已死，amd當立]Intel CPU設計有漏洞，修復會導致性能大幅下降","createTime":"2018-01-03T13:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T08:34:12.000Z","uid":41887,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"be6ff689d6c07efb819f39dbcdcafe84e6c3f377","tid":518569,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:10:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theregister.co.uk/2018/01/02/intel_cpu_design_flaw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theregister.co.uk%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2Fintel_cpu_design_flaw%2F&d=Wopcp%2FV0PR%2FWj2kd24BNmOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=48f42d5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theregister.co.uk/2018/01/02/intel_cpu_design_flaw/</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">'Kernel memory leaking' Intel processor design flaw forces Linux, Windows redesign</span></strong><br />\n<strong>Other OSes will need an update, performance hits loom</strong><br />\n<br />\nsummary<br />\n- Intel hardware design 有問題，導致user code可以access到kernel address space，有人<strong>推測</strong>係speculative execution導致一d未做privilege check既instruction可以execute<br />\n- 主流os包括windows、linux、macos都會受影響<br />\n- update microcode 不足以解決問題，要係os level上落patch<br />\n- 目前linux既做法係KPTI(kernel page table isolation)，即係將kernel address space完全isolate出去，但係咁樣會導致每次user mode &lt;-&gt; kernel mode 既切換(例如system call同hardware interrupt) 都要換page table，導致cpu要洗走cache，非常慢<br />\n- PostgreSQL做過性能測試，最好情況下降17%，最壞情況下降23%<br />\n- 根據linux kernel mailing list，amd不受影響"},{"pid":"c6278e03ed47756e8489b884cd93803cdbb5dadd","tid":518569,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:15:57.000Z","msg":"FFmpeg，PostgreSQL，Redis性能測試by <a href=\"http://www.phoronix.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.phoronix.com&d=Wopcp%2FV0PR%2FWj2kd24BNmOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=f741b171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.phoronix.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.phoronix.co